fr.epita.iam.datamodels

Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.epita.iam.datamodels.Identity

  • public class Identity
extends java.lang.Object

    Description

    This class allows to create an Identity for persisting it later if needed, it has parameters as uid, email, and displayName which can be set, and an int id which should be set with the DB index only

    Author:
    Stéfano Acosta - Álvaro Bilbao
